64.5	Seven_Samurai	Seven Samurai	Seven Samurai Shichinin no Samurai) is a 1954 Japanese adventure drama film co-written, edited, and directed by Akira Kurosawa. The film takes place in 1587 during the Warring States Period of Japan. It follows the story of a village of farmers that hire seven masterless samurai to combat bandits who will return after the harvest to steal their crops.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/Seven_Samurai_poster.jpg/215px-Seven_Samurai_poster.jpg
